==English==

===Etymology===
{{L.}} & NL ''[[trilogia]]'' from {{Gk.}} '''[[tri]]''' (meaning "three") + ''[[-logia]]'' ([[-logy]])

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg-y|trilog|y}}

# A collection of three books, motion pictures, or electronic games in one. A three-part series.

